control flow do

              call :a7, :subprocess, parameters: { :label => "prepare for venepuncture", :method => :post, :arguments => [⭐(:name => :behavior, :value => "wait_running" ), ⭐(:name => :url, :value => nil ), ⭐(:name => :init, :value => nil ), ⭐(:name => :endpoints, :value => nil ), ⭐(:name => :attributes, :value => nil ), ⭐(:name => :customization, :value => nil )], :annotations => { :_generic => {:Resource => "data.assigned_resource"}, :_timing => {:_timing_weight => nil, :_timing_avg => nil, :explanations => nil}, :_shifting => {:_shifting_type => "Duration"}, :_context_data_analysis => {:probes => nil, :ips => nil}, :report => {:url => nil}, :_notes => {:_notes_general => nil} } }
              call :a8, nil, parameters: { :label => "venepuncture", :method => :post, :arguments => nil, :annotations => { :_generic => {:Resource => "data.assigned_resource"}, :_timing => {:_timing_weight => nil, :_timing_avg => nil, :explanations => nil}, :_shifting => {:_shifting_type => "Duration"}, :_context_data_analysis => {:probes => nil, :ips => nil}, :report => {:url => nil}, :_notes => {:_notes_general => nil} } }
              call :a9, nil, parameters: { :label => "collect blood", :method => :post, :arguments => nil, :annotations => { :_generic => {:Resource => nil}, :_timing => {:_timing_weight => nil, :_timing_avg => nil, :explanations => nil}, :_shifting => {:_shifting_type => "Duration"}, :_context_data_analysis => {:probes => nil, :ips => nil}, :report => {:url => nil}, :_notes => {:_notes_general => nil} } }
              parallel :wait => 1, :cancel => :first do
                parallel_branch do |local|
                  call :a10, nil, parameters: { :label => "monitor patient", :method => :post, :arguments => nil, :annotations => { :_generic => nil, :_timing => {:_timing_weight => nil, :_timing_avg => nil, :explanations => nil}, :_shifting => {:_shifting_type => "Duration"}, :_context_data_analysis => {:probes => nil, :ips => nil}, :report => {:url => nil}, :_notes => {:_notes_general => nil} } }
                end

                parallel_branch do |local|
                  call :a10, nil, parameters: { :label => "monitor patient", :method => :post, :arguments => nil, :annotations => { :_generic => nil, :_timing => {:_timing_weight => nil, :_timing_avg => nil, :explanations => nil}, :_shifting => {:_shifting_type => "Duration"}, :_context_data_analysis => {:probes => nil, :ips => nil}, :report => {:url => nil}, :_notes => {:_notes_general => nil} } }

        parallel_branch do |local|
          call :a4, nil, parameters: { :label => "check respondent bank certificate", :method => :post, :arguments => nil, :annotations => { :_generic => nil, :_timing => {:_timing_weight => nil, :_timing_avg => nil, :explanations => nil}, :_shifting => {:_shifting_type => "Duration"}, :_context_data_analysis => {:probes => nil, :ips => nil}, :report => {:url => nil}, :_notes => {:_notes_general => nil} } }, finalize: <<-END

        parallel_branch do |local|
          loop pre_test("data.evaluation_extra") do
            call :a6, nil, parameters: { :label => "conduct due diligence study", :method => :post, :arguments => nil, :annotations => { :_generic => nil, :_timing => {:_timing_weight => nil, :_timing_avg => nil, :explanations => nil}, :_shifting => {:_shifting_type => "Duration"}, :_context_data_analysis => {:probes => nil, :ips => nil}, :report => {:url => nil}, :_notes => {:_notes_general => nil} } }, finalize: <<-END
              data.evaluation = result
              data.evaluation_extra = result

            choose :exclusive do
              alternative test("!data.evaluation") do
                call :a8, nil, parameters: { :label => "Lookup Partner Banks", :method => :post, :arguments => nil, :annotations => { :_generic => nil, :_timing => {:_timing_weight => nil, :_timing_avg => nil, :explanations => nil}, :_shifting => {:_shifting_type => "Duration"}, :_context_data_analysis => {:probes => nil, :ips => nil}, :report => {:url => nil}, :_notes => {:_notes_general => nil} } }
              end
            end
          end
        end
      end
      choose :exclusive do
        alternative test("not data.evaluation") do
          call :a7, nil, parameters: { :label => "add respondent bank to blacklist", :method => :post, :arguments => nil, :annotations => { :_generic => nil, :_timing => {:_timing_weight => nil, :_timing_avg => nil, :explanations => nil}, :_shifting => {:_shifting_type => "Duration"}, :_context_data_analysis => {:probes => nil, :ips => nil}, :report => {:url => nil}, :_notes => {:_notes_general => nil} } }
        end

  end
  call :a9, nil, parameters: { :label => "obtain respondent bank annual report", :method => :post, :arguments => nil, :annotations => { :_generic => nil, :_timing => {:_timing_weight => nil, :_timing_avg => nil, :explanations => nil}, :_shifting => {:_shifting_type => "Duration"}, :_context_data_analysis => {:probes => nil, :ips => nil}, :report => {:url => nil}, :_notes => {:_notes_general => nil} } }
  parallel :wait => -1, :cancel => :last do
    parallel_branch do |local|
      call :a10, nil, parameters: { :label => "analyze respondent bank annual report", :method => :post, :arguments => nil, :annotations => { :_generic => nil, :_timing => {:_timing_weight => nil, :_timing_avg => nil, :explanations => nil}, :_shifting => {:_shifting_type => "Duration"}, :_context_data_analysis => {:probes => nil, :ips => nil}, :report => {:url => nil}, :_notes => {:_notes_general => nil} } }
    end
    parallel_branch do |local|

      choose :exclusive do
        alternative test("data.respondent_bank_rating == \"rejected\"") do
          call :a12, nil, parameters: { :label => "handle rejection", :method => :post, :arguments => nil, :annotations => { :_generic => nil, :_timing => {:_timing_weight => nil, :_timing_avg => nil, :explanations => nil}, :_shifting => {:_shifting_type => "Duration"}, :_context_data_analysis => {:probes => nil, :ips => nil}, :report => {:url => nil}, :_notes => {:_notes_general => nil} } }
          terminate
        end
      end
    end
  end
  choose :exclusive do
    alternative test("data.record or (data.eval and data.rating)") do
      call :a3, nil, parameters: { :label => "Open Correspondent Account", :method => :post, :arguments => nil, :annotations => { :_generic => nil, :_timing => {:_timing_weight => nil, :_timing_avg => nil, :explanations => nil}, :_shifting => {:_shifting_type => "Duration"}, :_context_data_analysis => {:probes => nil, :ips => nil}, :report => {:url => nil}, :_notes => {:_notes_general => nil} } }
    end
  end
